00:55:02,207 --> 00:55:04,846
Now it's getting really windy
where we are.

474
00:55:04,927 --> 00:55:07,885
We'll be pretty lucky to
stay with them through this.

475
00:55:07,967 --> 00:55:10,242
We'll give a good try, though.

