00:55:59,527 --> 00:56:01,916
Four... Four I can see.

491
00:56:02,007 --> 00:56:06,319
ATTENBOROUGH: A change in the weather
gives the chance to film at last.

492
00:56:07,727 --> 00:56:11,800
They've gone further up this way.
